235
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:06,309
di PICTURE

236
00:11:06,309 --> 00:11:07,732
iz fun Poyln.

237
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:10,736
dos iz mayn shvester, Miryem.

238
00:11:11,012 --> 00:11:13,076
zi hot gemakht di PICTURE

239
00:11:13,076 --> 00:11:14,584
far der milkhome,

240
00:11:15,079 --> 00:11:18,836
kedey tsu shikn tsum onkl keyn Yisroel.

241
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,872
er hot zi gevolt aroysnemen,

242
00:11:20,872 --> 00:11:22,683
nor s'iz aroys di milkhome,

243
00:11:22,909 --> 00:11:24,120
iz zi geblibn

244
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,142
un m'hot zi geshosn in Opalin.

245
00:11:30,604 --> 00:11:32,066
di PICTURE

246
00:11:32,123 --> 00:11:33,939
iz fun far der milkhome,

247
00:11:34,165 --> 00:11:37,230
vi mayn bruder hot gehat a, a maysterskay.

248
00:11:37,354 --> 00:11:41,932
⟨es iz⟩ do do oyf der PICTURE er, un, un s'iz do der anderer bruder, Hershl,

249
00:11:41,932 --> 00:11:43,755
ven er hot im gelernt arbetn,

250
00:11:43,755 --> 00:11:45,212
mit an arbetorer.

251
00:11:46,568 --> 00:11:47,909
der bruder

252
00:11:48,289 --> 00:11:51,101
hot mir gegibn di PICTURE shoyn do in Amerike.

253
00:11:55,782 --> 00:11:58,999
di PICTURE iz fun far der milkhome in Poyln.

254
00:11:59,342 --> 00:12:00,770
do bin ikh do,

255
00:12:01,654 --> 00:12:03,437
un s'iz do mayn bruder,

256
00:12:03,544 --> 00:12:04,891
mayn kuzine,

257
00:12:04,891 --> 00:12:05,935
Fride,

258
00:12:06,379 --> 00:12:08,516
un mayn COUSIN, HENRY.

259
00:12:08,927 --> 00:12:12,191
zogt mir, fun der rekhter zayt, ver shteyt dortn?

260
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:14,271
fun der rekhter zayt

261
00:12:14,378 --> 00:12:15,367
bin i-...

262
00:12:15,897 --> 00:12:16,929
yene zayt?

263
00:12:16,929 --> 00:12:19,006
yene zayt, dos iz der COUSIN, HENRY,

264
00:12:19,006 --> 00:12:22,556
un nokh im shteyt der bruder, Hershl, di kuzine, Fride,

265
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:24,074
un do bin ikh.

266
00:12:24,081 --> 00:12:26,232
dos iz geven far der milkhome,

267
00:12:26,393 --> 00:12:30,150
gef-, gefo- fotografirt bay undz in shtetl Opalin.

268
00:12:31,303 --> 00:12:33,592
vi hot ir bakumen dem PICTURE?

269
00:12:35,961 --> 00:12:40,151
dos, di ale PICTURES hob ikh gehaltn mit zikh in ale tsores,

270
00:12:40,151 --> 00:12:41,388
un ikh hob nisht gevolt,

271
00:12:41,395 --> 00:12:44,933
⟨ikh⟩ zol blaybn on a PICTURE, ⟨zikh ge-⟩ kukn oyf mayne eygene.

272
00:12:48,212 --> 00:12:51,564
di PICTURE iz far der milkhome, oyfn Bug,

273
00:12:52,043 --> 00:12:54,635
ven m'hot geshtanen, di,

274
00:12:55,182 --> 00:12:58,281
di tratves, vos me fleg avekshikn dos holts,

275
00:12:58,641 --> 00:13:00,137
ho'mir zikh fotografirt.

276
00:13:00,261 --> 00:13:02,451
oyf der rekhter zayt shteyt mayn khaver,

277
00:13:02,451 --> 00:13:03,832
Yankl Sidel,

278
00:13:04,227 --> 00:13:07,073
un dort shteyt Froyem Furman,

279
00:13:11,483 --> 00:13:13,789
ikh bin do, un nokh eyner a khaver

280
00:13:13,913 --> 00:13:15,020
fun Opalin.

281
00:13:18,756 --> 00:13:22,464
di PICTURE iz far der milkhome, oykhet oyfn vaser gemakht,

282
00:13:22,519 --> 00:13:26,852
mit di tratves. ⟨kh-⟩ un, fun rekhts iz Y- Yankl Sidel...

283
00:13:26,852 --> 00:13:29,026
er hot gevoynt in Yisroel, hot er gevoynt...

284
00:13:29,050 --> 00:13:31,288
un, un do shtey ikh oykhet.

285
00:13:31,446 --> 00:13:34,207
di PICTURE oykhet geven mit mir di gantse tsayt,

286
00:13:34,365 --> 00:13:35,692
⟨⟩, fun der milkhome.

287
00:13:48,777 --> 00:13:51,302
dos iz di PICTURE, ven m'hot mir

288
00:13:51,780 --> 00:13:54,173
aropgenumen ven ikh bin gelign in bet

289
00:13:54,173 --> 00:13:56,600
in Saratov, in HOSPITAL.

290
00:13:56,691 --> 00:13:58,502
dos iz geven in nayntsn

291
00:13:58,502 --> 00:13:59,999
fir un fertsik,

292
00:13:59,999 --> 00:14:01,363
nokhn farvund⟨er⟩n.

293
00:14:14,832 --> 00:14:17,154
dos iz di PICTURE gemakht gevorn

294
00:14:17,953 --> 00:14:19,482
in Tshernevits:

295
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:22,869
mayn froy, un mayn

296
00:14:22,869 --> 00:14:24,463
meydele Khane,

297
00:14:24,463 --> 00:14:26,536
ven zi iz nokh geven a kleyne, un ikh bin do.

298
00:14:26,468 --> 00:14:28,050
ayer froy, vi heyst?

299
00:14:26,543 --> 00:14:27,780
dos...

300
00:14:27,780 --> 00:14:30,401
heyst, mayn froy heyst Mindl.

301
00:14:37,292 --> 00:14:40,053
dos iz a artikl, geven in "Forverts,"

302
00:14:40,144 --> 00:14:43,344
in, nayntsn fir un zibetsik, FEBRUARY.

303
00:14:45,426 --> 00:14:47,141
demolst hot geshribn

304
00:14:47,839 --> 00:14:50,375
in der tsaytung mister Shmulevitsh.

305
00:14:50,375 --> 00:14:52,434
ven ikh hob geleyent dem "Forverts,"

306
00:14:52,434 --> 00:14:55,159
hob ikh ibergeleyent, iz geven dort a artikl

307
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:58,545
fun a POLICEMAN vos er iz geven bay undz in LYUBOML'

308
00:14:59,348 --> 00:15:01,721
in, in get- bay der geto.

309
00:15:01,980 --> 00:15:03,888
er hot geheysn KOVAL'CHUK.

310
00:15:03,888 --> 00:15:06,261
der POLICEMAN iz gekumen

311
00:15:06,570 --> 00:15:09,999
dortn, aroysgefirt a yid

312
00:15:10,097 --> 00:15:12,183
on a fus, mit a froy.

313
00:15:12,747 --> 00:15:16,040
un ikh bin gelign in dem bunker, hob ikh gehert

314
00:15:16,040 --> 00:15:18,951
vi zi hot im gebetn: "mister,

315
00:15:19,041 --> 00:15:21,353
 KOVAL'CHUK,

316
00:15:21,353 --> 00:15:23,946
du kenst dokh undz, du host dokh bay undz gearbet.

317
00:15:24,205 --> 00:15:28,131
loz undz iber, tshepe nisht." hot er gezogt, "ikh bin nisht keyn,

318
00:15:28,131 --> 00:15:31,421
yetst keyn PAN⟨IE⟩ KOVAL'CHUK. ikh bin yetst a POLICEMAN

319
00:15:31,478 --> 00:15:33,277
un ikh darf aykh firn shisn."

320
00:15:33,402 --> 00:15:35,421
un er hot avekgenumen di mentshn.

321
00:15:36,507 --> 00:15:41,545
tsi er hot zey geshosn, hob ikh nisht gezen. un dos bi- iz, hot men geshribn in tsaytung,

322
00:15:41,545 --> 00:15:43,490
un ikh hob gedorfn zayn a eydes

323
00:15:43,490 --> 00:15:47,131
barn sud un zogn az, dos iz der KOVAL'CHUK.

324
00:15:47,131 --> 00:15:50,313
hot men, dos iz fun, der artikl fun dem tsaytung.

325
00:15:56,959 --> 00:15:59,715
di PICTURE hot men gemakht shoyn do in Amerike.

326
00:15:59,715 --> 00:16:00,727
do shteyt

327
00:16:00,727 --> 00:16:03,414
di eltere tokhter mayne, Khane JA⟨C⟩OB,

328
00:16:04,249 --> 00:16:05,913
der tsveyter shtey ikh,

329
00:16:06,072 --> 00:16:08,783
di drite shteyt mayn froy, Mindl Melamed,

330
00:16:09,143 --> 00:16:14,233
un do, un di letste iz mayn klenere tokhter, Zoye Sapir.

331
00:16:19,842 --> 00:16:24,151
 bite, shtelt zikh for, un ver zitst mit aykh oykh?

332
00:16:23,858 --> 00:16:25,590
ikh bin Leyzer Melamed.

333
00:16:25,613 --> 00:16:27,651
mit mir zitst mayn froy,

334
00:16:27,651 --> 00:16:29,313
Mindl Melamed.

